<!--<h4>First Face.</h4>-->

<p>
<lb n="1"/>svastiśrī vijayābhyu 
<lb n="2" break="no"/>daya śālivāhana śa 
<lb n="3" break="no"/>ka varṣaṁbulu Agu 
<lb n="4"/>1461 Agunēṁṭi vi 
<lb n="5" break="no"/>kāri [ saṁvatsara bhādra 
<lb n="6" break="no"/>pada śu ka lu ]
<lb n="7"/>mahārājādhirā 
<lb n="8" break="no"/>ja rājaparamēśvara 
<lb n="9"/>śrīvīrapratāpa 
<lb n="10"/>śrī Acyutadēvama 
<lb n="11" break="no"/>hādēvarāya 
<lb n="12" break="no"/>luṁgāru vija<supplied reason="omitted">ya</supplied>na 
<lb n="13" break="no"/><unclear>gara</unclear> maṁdu <unclear>pṛti</unclear> 
</p>

<!--<h4>Second Face.</h4>-->

<p>
<lb n="14-38"/><ce>damaged</ce>
<lb n="39"/>varasidhivinā 
<lb n="40" break="no"/>yaka dēvara<unclear>ku</unclear> 
<lb n="41-48"/><ce>damaged</ce>
</p>

